name: FoodFavors
0:
”Alexa, tell Food Favors my favorite food is tacos”
”My favorite food is pizza”
”What is my favorite food?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food favors
des: Through this Skill, you can interact with Alexa and share your favorite food! Tell Alexa what your favorite food is, by saying something like, "My favorite food is pizza." Alexa will remember this, and if you ask Alexa something like "What is my favorite food?" Alexa will say it back to you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
